{"tid":2331562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"FB「北區」group 因為18年一句說話批評中港問題 被Fuckbook封鎖 原group人請訂‘北區2.0’","createTime":"2020-12-19T01:47:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T05:22:09.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c8ec24ef1cf11e4eafbd9d8bb233d32af7de7f88","tid":2331562,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T01:47:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CmrCXYx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCmrCXYx.png&h=d0780ffd&s={SIZE}\" />今日（週五）下午二時，擁有約五萬多名成員的群組「北區」被Facebook封鎖，是繼「大埔」、「天下貓貓一樣貓」及「小心駕駛」等大型群組的新封殺對象。<br />\n<br />\n隨後本報記者致電群組擁有人Alex查詢，得知其封殺原因僅因為2018年曾於留言中批評中港問題，可能觸碰到管理Facebook亞太區的中國職員心靈才導致被封群，Alex又稱對Facebook日趨嚴重的網絡言論審查感到無奈，認為嚴重影響社交媒體應有的流通性。<br />\n<br />\n而Alex於傍晚五時已開設「北區2.0」，呼籲原有群組成員加入，他又稱不擔心再被封殺，大不了封一開十。<br />\n<br />\n記者：廖宇行 <br />\n製圖：新界北咆哮虐殺龍<br />\n<br />\n#邊境 #邊境媒體 #社區媒體 #北區 #上水 #粉嶺 #聯和墟 #莫須有 #言論自由 <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n北區各大型群組fb及mewe連結：<br />\n<br />\n北區2.0:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1005890809910460/permalink/1005891349910406/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1005890809910460%2Fpermalink%2F1005891349910406%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBSrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=5f9ef025\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1005890809910460/permalink/1005891349910406/</a><br />\nMewe:<br />\n<a href=\"https://mewe.com/join/北區20northdistrict20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmewe.com%2Fjoin%2F%E5%8C%97%E5%8D%8020northdistrict20&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBSrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=bbad5c10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mewe.com/join/北區20northdistrict20</a><br />\n<br />\n真.上水粉嶺人大聯盟：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/2421951494701498/\" da